title: DVD-Fireplace and DVD-Aquarium [DVD] -superlarsi.
description:
DVD-Fireplace
Convert your TV to a beautiful and crackling fireplace and choose between fire/hearth sounds or classical music in surround-sound. Requires no wood-chopping and never burns out. Playtime: 45 minutes. Perfect atmosphere enhancer!

-----

DVD-Aquarium
Convert your TV to a beatiful aquarium and choose between aquarium sounds or classical music in surround-sound. The fishes never need feeding nor does the aquarium ever need cleaning. Playtime: 40 minutes. Perfect atmosphere enhancer!

-----

There are 2 iso files. One for the Fireplace and one for the Aquarium.
